    "This dataset spans languages including English, French, German, and Arabic.",
    "• AESLC (Zhang and Tetreault, 2019).",
    "The AESLC dataset is formed by aggregating email messages from employees at Enron Corporation.",
    "The objective is to generate concise summaries for the textual content found in the email subjects.",
    "The creators argue that, in contrast to news articles where the initial and concluding sentences typically offer a summarizing overview of the article, the email domain presents a more challenging context."
